Mom, let's talk in peace.

275
00:21:57,700 --> 00:22:00,000
The time when I returned home to apply for a visa,

276
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:03,000
he was released and I came across him.

277
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,600
I didn't intend to stay.

278
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:10,600
