302
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:17,400
- You're right. 
 - Now that you know...

303
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:20,500
He just can't change the firmness in his bones,

304
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,400
no matter how long it has been,

305
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:25,300
