327
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:56,140
So you are here to support Li Xun?

328
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,100
Yeah.

329
00:24:57,100 --> 00:25:01,280
Today, I want to represent him as his elder to chat with you.

330
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:02,520
