400
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:58,360
My daughter never made any mistakes since childhood.

401
00:29:58,360 --> 00:30:01,840
Her husband should be clean as well.

402
00:30:01,840 --> 00:30:03,920
That's not too much, right?

403
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:10,620
If you can do something to clean up the stains on your file

404
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:16,100
and invite your parents to sit together with us to talk it over.

405
00:30:16,100 --> 00:30:18,530
I think I can agree.

406
00:30:18,530 --> 00:30:20,380
What's your opinion?

407
00:30:34,070 --> 00:30:35,690
Aunt.

408
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:42,630
Zhu Yun has the ability to change the world.

409
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:46,900
