410
00:30:48,550 --> 00:30:50,460
You, you.

411
00:30:50,460 --> 00:30:52,340
What did you say?

412
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,730
It depends on you, Dad.

413
00:31:18,290 --> 00:31:20,110
I will try.

414
00:31:36,830 --> 00:31:38,660
Are you hungry?

415
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:44,310
There is a good noodle restaurant nearby.

416
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:46,380
I'll treat you.

417
00:32:05,690 --> 00:32:07,930
You didn't leave?

418
00:32:07,930 --> 00:32:09,800
I have been here all the time.

419
00:32:12,210 --> 00:32:17,050
Your mother is so good and forthright, why was her daughter so timid?

420
00:32:17,050 --> 00:32:19,070
I wasn't timid.

421
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:20,590
But don't blame her.

422
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:24,040
She has been a teacher for decades. This is her thinking inertia.

423
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:26,250
