428
00:32:54,770 --> 00:32:57,230
What are you reading?

429
00:32:57,230 --> 00:32:58,420
That book you gave me.

430
00:32:58,420 --> 00:33:00,050
Is it nice?

431
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,580
Not bad.

432
00:33:06,050 --> 00:33:07,880
Zhu Yun.

